    <p class="text-gray-300">If <span class="math">e_1</span> didn't occur, the <span class="math">\\widetilde{\\mathsf{R}}^{\\langle \\mathsf{N},2\\cdot \\mathsf{h} - 1\\rangle}(m_{2^{\\prime}\\cdot h - 1}^{\\prime})</span> call is fresh, so the probability it hits the value on the right hand side is exactly <span class="math">1 / p</span>.</p>

